---
// TrustSignals.astro
// Tier 1 + Tier 2 trust signals from research/03 §3
// No testimonials (no clients yet). No promised returns.
// Paper trading as feature (§10).
---

<section id="trust" class="py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-[#0d1117]">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-16 max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-teal-400 text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Why Trust Us</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight">
        Transparency Is the Product
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
        This is a research project — everything is checkable,
        not marketing copy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Tier 1 technical trust signals -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-12">

      <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/4 border border-white/8 p-5 hover:border-white/15 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-500/10 border border-teal-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#14b8a6" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 21 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 5.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 21 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 5.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 21 11.25v7.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Paper Track Record</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/40 leading-relaxed">
          Paper trading started June 10, 2026. Day counter, equity curve, and all trades
          are public. No cherry-picked windows.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/4 border border-white/8 p-5 hover:border-white/15 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-500/10 border border-accent-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 1 0-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Deterministic Risk Engine</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/40 leading-relaxed">
          RiskPolicy v1.0 is a hard-coded gate with published parameters. Cannot be
          overridden by any agent, strategy, or human. Kill switch at 5% drawdown.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/4 border border-white/8 p-5 hover:border-white/15 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.5)" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 0 0-9-9Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Open Methodology</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/40 leading-relaxed">
          Strategy logic, risk parameters, adapter registry, and tournament evaluator
          are all documented. Every change is a git commit.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/4 border border-white/8 p-5 hover:border-white/15 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-500/10 border border-accent-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 12 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 3 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1 1.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0 1 12 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 1.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 21 12Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Audited Protocols Only</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/40 leading-relaxed">
          We only monitor protocols with multiple independent audits. T1 protocols
          (Aave, Morpho, Compound) have 5+ audits. T2 capped at 50% of portfolio.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Paper trading as feature — narrative section -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500/5 to-teal-500/5 border border-white/10 p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-xs text-accent-400 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Data IS the Social Proof</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
          We're building the honest paper track record first.
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Most DeFi yield products ask you to trust them. We're asking you to watch us first.
          For 30+ days before any real capital, our strategy runs against live market data —
          every rebalance logged, every risk gate enforced, every underperforming protocol replaced.
          When we go live, you'll know exactly what you're getting into.
        </p>
        <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-accent-500/50 pl-4 italic text-white/40 text-sm">
          "We built the risk policy so that even when we want to override it — we cannot."
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Specificity metrics — numbers that signal honesty -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
      {[
        { value: '27/29', label: 'Go-live criteria', detail: 'NOT READY (2 blockers)' },
        { value: 'Several', label: 'Protocols monitored', detail: 'Live read-only adapters' },
        { value: '$5M', label: 'TVL floor per pool', detail: 'Hard policy limit' },
        { value: '5%', label: 'Drawdown kill switch', detail: 'Non-overridable' },
      ].map(({ value, label, detail }) => (
        <div class="text-center py-6 px-4 rounded-xl border border-white/8 bg-white/2">
          <div class="text-3xl font-mono font-bold text-white mb-1">{value}</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/50 font-medium mb-1">{label}</div>
          <div class="text-[11px] text-white/25">{detail}</div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
